But it turns out that he was left of the place for such operators and that they could have a real success.
We are no longer obliged to go too far to find examples.
In February we informed you of the launch, in Poland, of the virtual Mobilking operator.
In only six months, this operator managed to win over 100 thousand customers and become the fifth operator of the country.
We add that behind the Mobilking, there is the Penta financial group, which has the U:fon in Czech.
The advantage of virtual operators is the possibility of focusing on a much more specific target group.
